data.description: Amazing 4BR/2BA full brick home in Alabaster! This spacious home features large rooms with vaulted/cathedral ceilings, a beautiful fireplace, separate dining room, a cozy chef's kitchen and a main level laundry. The master suite features 2 walk in closets, a soaking tub, separate shower. 3 more large bedrooms and another large full bath. A main level garage and fenced yard complete this wonderful home. Interior photographs are forthcoming.
